    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This unique stance can only be activated if you have an active seal created by the Ma'en Juts: En'mi technique.<br><br>In this stance, you gain a ranged touch attack with a range of 10 ft, which uses your Intelligence modifier to hit (instead of your Dexterity modifier) and deals 1d6 fire damage. These attacks are considered unarmed attacks to determine the number of attacks you can make.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> At ECL 8 or higher, you can spend 2 Chakra to increase the damage to 1d8. At ECL 16 or higher, you can spend 4 Chakra to increase the damage to 2d6. Mastery does not apply to your ECL for this.</p>\n<p><b>Mastery:</b> The third step increases the range of the attacks to 15 ft if they have been empowered to deal 1d8 damage. The fifth step increases the range to 20 ft if they have been empowered to 2d6.</p>\n",
